The message has already received more than 2,000 'likes'.

Leo and Lulu, whose full name was Lucia, were murdered at the family's Upper West Side home on October 26 in an horrific crime that shocked the country.

Mrs Krim arrived home at the family apartment to find two of her two children dead in the bath-tub next to nanny Yoselyn Ortega who had slit her own throat in an alleged suicide attempt.

